# Git-tracked development overlay (non-secret differences only).
# Keep this file small and only put dev-specific differences vs `.env`.
#
# Load order:
# `.env` -> `.env.dev` -> `.env.local` -> `.env.dev.local`
#
# Examples (uncomment only if needed):
# WORKFLOW_LOCAL_DATA_DIR="/tmp/open-agents-workflow-local-dev"
# SANDBOX_ROOT_DIR="/tmp/open-agents-sandboxes-dev"
